OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThe evening
OL,6,Fwill continue cloudy with showery
OL,7,Foutbreaks of rain. This will begin to
OL,8,Fclear from late evening with clear
OL,9,Fspells increasing later in the night.
OL,10,
OL,11,CSunday:FThe morning will begin dry
OL,12,Fwith bright or sunny spells. Scattered
OL,13,Fshowers will build from mid-morning.
OL,14,
OL,15,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FBright
OL,16,Fand mostly dry Monday becoming cloudy
OL,17,Fwith occasionally heavy and showery
OL,18,Frain Tuesday and Wednesday.
